rows.label: qev087104_MSG0001
rows.name: I received your report. Good work collecting those samples.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0002
rows.name: I'm just sorry we weren't able to get more.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0003
rows.name: We'll take what we can get. You have my thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0005
rows.name:
If we can forge an alliance,
I'm certain they'll be friends we can trust.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0006
rows.name:
I'll remember that. And should the day come,
I'd like you to serve as ambassador.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0007
rows.name:
My pleasure.
As long as you don't send me there to declare war.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0009
rows.name: The fewer enemies we have, the easier my job is.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0011
rows.name: That was quite the sample collection. Excellent work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0013
rows.name:
If we can forge an alliance,
I'm certain they'll be friends we can trust.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0015
rows.name:
And should that day come,
would you consider serving as ambassador?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0016
rows.name: Of course. As long as you don't send me there to declare war.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0018
rows.name: The fewer enemies we have, the easier my job is.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087104_MSG0019
rows.name:
You have my thanks.
Now go and rest up until your next mission.[ST:wait ]
